These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, chess, drawing, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, journalist, firefighter, police-officer
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the firefighter and the journalist##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the firefighter is not to the left of the firefighter##8
4. the journalist is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | reading  | camping | drawing | chess  |
| Job   | coach | firefighter   | police-officer  | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, camping, writing, chess
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the journalist##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is camping##2
5. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby   | writing | camping          | chess | puzzles     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

