.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, broccoli, potato, cucumber
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person eating potato##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating peas##1
4. the person eating broccoli is in an even position##4
5. the person eating cucumber is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating peas is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the person eating cucumber is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food           | peas | broccoli | potato     | cucumber |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

