.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, oliveros, cain, tiparillo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | cain   | oliveros         | tiparillo   | pall-mall    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

