.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino, go, whist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing domino##7
2. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person playing whist is somewhere between the person playing go and the person playing mah-jongg##7
4. the person playing go is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person playing domino and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Game   | domino   | go | whist | mah-jongg    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

