.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, kiwi, lettuce, pineapple
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, nigerian, colombian, spanish
1. the spanish is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the turkish is on the left or right of the colombian##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the nigerian##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| Nationality   | nigerian   | spanish         | colombian | turkish |

