.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, black, purple, turquise
1. the person who likes black is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the person who likes turquise is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person who likes purple##7
3. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
4. the person who likes turquise is not to the left of the person who likes orange##8
5. the person who likes turquise is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola      | sprite | almond-milk | water   |
| Color      | orange | purple | turquise  | black |

