.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, july, october
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, rugby, tennis
1. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's birthday is in september##7
5. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
6. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's birthday is in july##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Birthday     | september | july | october | april     |
| Sport   | baseball   | rugby        | tennis          | ice-hockey |

