.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall, tiparillo, oliveros
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the blend-smoker##2
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the blend-smoker##5
5. the pall-mall-smoker is the pall-mall-smoker##1
6. the fan of indie is not the tiparillo-smoker##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the blend-smoker is not to the left of the pall-mall-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| Cigar     | oliveros | pall-mall       | blend  | tiparillo    |

