.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, onion, pineapple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, fantasy, disaster
1. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
2. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating onion is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
6. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
7. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lime        | pineapple | onion      | corn    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | fantasy   | thriller | disaster |

