2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
4. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating cabbage is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person eating lettuce##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
8. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | cabbage | lettuce         | pear    | plum       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

