.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: lemon, zucchini, strawberry, grapefruit
1. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking tea and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the person eating lemon is between the person eating zucchini and the person eating grapefruit##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage   | 7up     | almond-milk | tea        | sprite       |
| Food      | strawberry | zucchini  | lemon | grapefruit |

