.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, boat, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
 9. the person driving the taxi is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Transport   | skateboard | jet-ski  | boat     | taxi    |

