.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, avocado, grapefruit, peas
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle, hamster
1. the person eating grapefruit is the owner of the dog##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
3. the owner of the goat is the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the hamster is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person eating avocado is between the owner of the goat and the person eating peas##2
7. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | peas        | avocado | asparagus | grapefruit |
| Pet   | hamster | turtle | goat   | dog    |

