.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, cricket, tennis, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, jet-ski, trike
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
3. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is water-polo##7
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5
5. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
6. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
7. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Sport         | weightlifting  | water-polo | cricket  | tennis  |
| Transport   | bike | car   | trike | jet-ski |

