.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, accountant, videographer, engineer
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, subway, van
1. the person driving the jet-ski is not the doctor##6
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the engineer is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
4. the videographer is the person driving the car##1
5. the engineer is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the car##7
6. the engineer is on the left of the doctor##1
7. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the van and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job         | accountant    | engineer | doctor | videographer |
| Transport   | jet-ski | van      | subway     | car     |

 